        "TileImage": "$($repository 1d8a162f-b8fd-44e7-9a05-e52eb03d80d2).Image",
        "Description": "Ho-Ho-Ho, Santa here! I&apos;ve received reports that some of my elves have left the North Pole and are now living in Mendoza, working grueling jobs at a winery. I am infuriated that my elves would leave without my permission, so I am putting a hit on the three of them. Take them out by drowing them, pushing them off ledges, and blowing them up to make them experiance as much pain as possible. Cheers!",
